    "body": "### Problem\n\nAs far as I know we cannot get the window of buffer. Correct me if I'm wrong.\n\nThe only way right now is going through every window and call nvim_win_get_buf everytime and checking the result. It is 0(n) (n = number of window) and takes a bit of time to write and one can make error writing such util.\n\n\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nWhat if instead such basic feature would be provided by nvim with \\nvim_buf_get_win\\ ? It would be O(1), would be less error prone than writing your own mistake and simpler",
